{"tid":438471,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[Android 用家注意⚠️] 勒索軟體DoubleLocker現身，會同你加密同改埋密碼","createTime":"2017-10-17T03:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T07:24:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2f29195bb068244cb9e9d0a1587f5ae6bebf5e38","tid":438471,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"安全軟體公司ESET發現一隻新的Android勒索軟體DoubleLocker，一旦不慎下載開啟，即會加密用戶手機所有檔案或是變更手機密碼要求支付贖金。<br />\n<br />\nDoubleLocker源自銀行木馬程式，最常見的散佈方式是透過被駭網站冒充Adobe Flash Player更新，誘使用戶下載安裝。一旦啟動後，它會以啟動「Google Play Service」的無障礙功能為名，要求使用者許可。獲得許可後，它就會啟動裝置管理權限，在不經過使用者同意下讓自己成為Android手機Home主頁的應用程式。<br />\n<br />\nESET惡意軟體研究人員Luk&aacute;&scaron; &Scaron;tefank解釋，透過成為手機預設Home主頁程式，當使用者點擊Home鍵時，這隻勒索軟體就會立刻啟動，鎖住手機。而因為動用了無障礙服務，使用者並不知道他們已啟動勒索軟體。<br />\n<br />\n但是他們還是會看到常見的勒索訊息，要求受害者必須在24小時內支付0.0130比特幣（下圖，約54美元或1650台幣，視時價而定）。攻擊者並建議使用者不要移除或封鎖DoubleLocker，否則就無法救回檔案。（下圖，來源：ESET）<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/110428_af11afa471f8b9fe32cbc44b3a3b00e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F110428_af11afa471f8b9fe32cbc44b3a3b00e7.jpg&h=702edb8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/117490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F117490&d=4r1OJhd6hxEzagf6THXhUHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=32872b2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/117490</a></div>"},{"pid":"780afbf5bfddbcf4e4342ef969f3c3be22ab4910","tid":438471,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:07:41.000Z","msg":"DoubleLocker之所以得名，是因為它使用了兩種方法鎖住Android裝置。首先它利用AES加密演算法將裝置裏主要目錄的所有檔案加密。被它加密的檔案都會多了副檔名.cryeye。它另一個方法是變更裝置的PIN碼。新的PIN碼是隨機取得，既未儲存在裝置，也未寄到其他地方，唯有攻擊者遠端重設PIN碼才能還手機自由。研究人員指出，這也是第一次出現擁有兩種封鎖技倆的Android平台惡意程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。用戶支付贖金後，才能解密檔案或是救回Android裝置。"},{"pid":"b245e95552999ef6e8a3a91890e707c4a80d7528","tid":438471,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"研究人員指出，將手機回復出廠設定是唯一可清除DoubleLocker勒索軟體的方法。而刷過機的裝置還有另一招；使用者可以在未啟動勒索軟體之前，透過ADB (Android Debug Bridge)介面連接裝置進入除錯模式，移除儲存PIN的系統檔案，就能避免PIN碼變更鎖機的命運。最後使用者再回到安全模式，移除該惡意程式的裝置管理員權限後將之移除。"},{"pid":"58152be4cca948725b04c59382ba2954dda46e1c","tid":438471,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/odSWGPLEqt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FodSWGPLEqt0&d=4r1OJhd6hxEzagf6THXhUHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=be14abea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/odSWGPLEqt0</a>"},{"pid":"61bd2542dac09367888d737f26050dd1988a0afc","tid":438471,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"裝LINUX <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c5f7108a653bb545ab8fb711ba0c30f99b2a00","tid":438471,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw, iuser或an俠, 唔該養成良好嘅backup習慣"},{"pid":"f8935408066f816e6aa71d552eeefeebda0e9433","tid":438471,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安全軟體公司ESET發現一隻新的Android勒索軟體DoubleLocker，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一旦不慎下載開啟</span>，即會加密用戶手機所有檔案或是變更手機密碼要求支付贖金。</blockquote><br />\nok"},{"pid":"c110cfbb536f89b6cd9ffd29a2034f8cc1f6f5e9","tid":438471,"uid":33579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:20:13.000Z","msg":"留意左巴打好耐<br />\n巴打每次post windows同android既病毒新聞全部都要user自己download + 自己run埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇d勁d既病毒係唔使自己禁download button再加run埋就可以中毒既例子<